Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.80,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好猛诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.45,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么无人岛上还会有…有冻土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:35.81,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:38.54,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,根……根根本就顾不上找石碑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.08,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,没混题 就耗在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:42.91,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,春香 鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.19,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是好了点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.03,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,但体力已经消耗了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.52,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧找到石碑就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:51.99,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.16,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,石头和树枝?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.65,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备拿来干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是用啥通过什么怎么弄出来的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:05.45,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 这应该是指着石碑的方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:07.59,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要沿着这方向走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.53,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,就能找到石碑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:10.63,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:12.22,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的天气…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.43,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 Piyo能给我们想办法么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.43,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(253,335)}ぴよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.85,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.02,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Piyo介好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.02,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(283,335)}ぴよすけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.10,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,Piyo加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.10,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(290,335)}ぴよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.14,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大的海豹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.39,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是海象么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:32.21,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,海豹先生 Yahoo～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.51,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是海象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:34.73,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.41,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 春香快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.54,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,得…得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:02.02,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,千早酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春香!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Harukasan的石碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(290,335)}はるかさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嵌入了了春香的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.22,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,你在逗我么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.33,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有啊 真的下不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.82,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样把你丢在这里算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.78,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,这样可能比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.70,Amami,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 您俩的表情怎么都这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.60,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,诶!? 你有主意么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.92,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,这能行么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.06,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.50,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.98,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.17,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,50)\fs30\bord2}没中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.71,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,这是恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.31,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我也不知道的 真的不知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.59,Futami,,0000,0000,0000,,千早姐姐 这样拍不到脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.27,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.41,Kisaragi,,0000,0000,0000,,你能给我好好解释下吗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:20.08,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我真什么都不知道啊!!
